                     Installation
                    ==============

Requirements
------------
Python >= 2.0 from http://www.python.org/
libxml2 from http://xmlsoft.org/

For the GUI config tool webcleanerconf you need
FOX Toolkit >= 0.99.172 from http://www.cfdrc.com/FOX/fox.html and
FXPy >= 0.99.172 from http://fxpy.sourceforge.net/
(FXPy version must be the same as FOX version)

Setup
-----
To install, execute "python2 setup.py install".
Run "python2 setup.py install --help" for help on install options.

Now you can start the proxy by executing "webcleaner start".
